name: Ananya Mukherjee
feedback: Darjeeling was mesmerizing! The tea gardens and the view of Kanchenjunga were breathtaking. A must-visit for everyone!

name: Rohit Saha
feedback: The Sundarbans trip was an adventure of a lifetime. Exploring the mangroves and spotting the Royal Bengal Tiger was unforgettable.

name: Priya Banerjee
feedback: Kolkata has so much to offer! From the iconic Victoria Memorial to the bustling markets, every moment was delightful.

name: Soumitra Das
feedback: Visiting Shantiniketan was a cultural experience. The art and music made my trip memorable, and the campus is beautiful!

name: Sreya Ghosh
feedback: Bishnupur's terracotta temples were stunning. The craftsmanship is remarkable, and the local sweets are a treat!

name: Tanmay Chatterjee
feedback: Kalimpong is a hidden gem! The flower markets and the panoramic views are breathtaking. Perfect for a peaceful getaway.

name: Debjani Roy
feedback: Murshidabad's historical significance is fascinating! The architecture and stories of the Nawabs made this trip very special.

name: Subhashis Paul
feedback: Malda's mangoes are legendary! The trip was enjoyable, and the local culture is rich and vibrant.

name: Riya Sen
feedback: Howrah's famous bridge and the beautiful ghats make for a stunning visit. The river cruise was a highlight!

name: Koushik Dutta
feedback: Digha's beaches are perfect for a weekend escape. The sunset views were absolutely breathtaking!

name: Nandini Mukherjee
feedback: Gangtok is a beautiful hill station! The monasteries and the view from Tashi View Point were unforgettable.

name: Arindam Roy
feedback: Jaisamaldaha was a serene experience. The quiet surroundings and natural beauty were incredibly calming.
